title: The Gary Null Show
content:
Today, the latest in health and healing, including a very unusual way to lower prostate cancer risk, milk may increase... <!--more--> your risk of fractures, japanese mushroom extract and HPV, and black tea and citrus lowering ovarian cancer risk.
In the environmental segment, birds in trouble all over the world, from Environmental Health News.
And, a commentary from Global Research on massacres being accepted without challenge.
Also, the latest on our economies and a new study from Harvard about China.
